subject to those same copyrights. However, the content of the site belongs to mousebird 
consulting exclusively.</p>

</div>
</div>

</div>

</article>

    </main>
    {% include "partials/footer.njk" %}
    <script src="{{ '/assets/js/bundle.js' | url }}"></script>
</body>
